CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 7, 1963, pg. 22 reads: "The Champion Vikings - Kneeling: Cora Simpson, Beacia Webb, Cecelia Howard and Dolores Simpson. Standing: Janet Kendricks, Daisy Pettis, Lynn Redman, Nellie Simpkins, holding the trophy, Manager Lewis Turner; Wilma Cargile, Ernestine Banks, Eliazbeth Ivey and Elaine Crowell. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of twelve softball players of the Vikings team, kneeling, left to right, Dolores Simpson, Cora Simpson, Beacia Webb, Wilma Cargile, Cecelia Howard, and Ernestine Banks, standing, left to right, Elaine Crowell, Lynn Redman, Nellie Simkins, unknown man and woman, Lewis Turner, manager, Elizabeth Ivey, Daisy Pettis, and Janet Kendriks, gathered on playing field
